title: I Created the 90's Room of my Dreams!
author: Garrett Watts
description:
Get 50% OFF your first 6-bottle box http://bit.ly/BrightCellarsGarrettWatts. Bright Cellars is the monthly wine club that matches you with wine that you’ll love. Get started by taking the taste palate quiz to see your personalized matches!

I turned my sad little guest bedroom into the 90s room of my dreams and I had a very, very good time doing it. Enjoy! I love you. 

Part 1 of this 90's room video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8WW_jcSCd00
